@startuml room_status

title Room — Ciclo de Vida do Status

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEF2FF
  BorderColor #7070AA
  ArrowColor #555588
  FontSize 13
}
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam noteBorderColor #CCBB55

[*] --> AVAILABLE : create()

AVAILABLE   --> INACTIVE    : deactivate()
AVAILABLE   --> ARCHIVED    : archive()
AVAILABLE   --> MAINTENANCE : putUnderMaintenance()

INACTIVE    --> AVAILABLE   : activate()
INACTIVE    --> ARCHIVED    : archive()
INACTIVE    --> MAINTENANCE : putUnderMaintenance()

MAINTENANCE --> AVAILABLE   : activate()
MAINTENANCE --> INACTIVE    : deactivate()
MAINTENANCE --> ARCHIVED    : archive()

ARCHIVED    --> AVAILABLE   : restore()
ARCHIVED    --> DELETED     : delete()

DELETED --> [*]

note right of ARCHIVED
  ARCHIVED não pode ir para INACTIVE
  nem para MAINTENANCE.
  Lança InvalidStateException (422).
  Única origem válida para delete().
end note

note right of DELETED
  Estado terminal (soft delete).
  Nenhuma transição permitida.
  Somente alcançável via ARCHIVED.
end note

@enduml
